===Talking to Kaqemeex again===
* '''Player:''' Hello there.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Hello again, adventurer. You will need to speak to my fellow druid Sanfew in the village south of here to continue in your quest.
* '''Player:''' Okay, thanks.
